                     <interp inst="t17940219-54-off299" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17940219-54-cd300" type="crimeDate">6th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940219-54-off299 t17940219-54-cd300"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940219-54-off302 t17940219-54-cd300"></join>, a cotton gown unmade, value 15s. a cotton gown, value 15s. two yards of linen cloth, value 2s. two muslin handkerchiefs, value 3s. a linen apron, value 1s. 6d. a muslin apron, value 2s. a cotton half handkerchief, value 6d. the goods of 
                     <persName id="t17940219-54-victim578" type="victimName">
                        Elizabeth 
                        Beecroft
                     <interp inst="t17940219-54-victim578" type="surname" value="Beecroft"></interp>
